skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dover trails
des: Dover, MA has miles and miles of hiking and walking trails within town or in neighboring towns. Too many to choose from, so ask Dover Trails to suggest a hike or walk for you. Simply say "Alexa, ask Dover Trails to give me a hike".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
